dct_title_s: Map of Maumee River (lower portion) and Tenmile Creek Basins showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Maumee River (Lower portion) and Tenmile Creek Basins
dct_description_sm: Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Maumee River (lower portion) and Tenmile Creek Basins and the quality of underground water.
